tDef(104, "Defeat all three enemies!") -- _t
tDef(104, "Get ready!") -- _t
tDef(112, "#LIGHT_GREEN#*The Cornac rogue comes back from the shadows*#WHITE#\
Well done, @playerdescriptor.race@! I knew you had potential.\
